prefix /api/v1/

Account Controller
/signup POST
/login POST
/logout GET

CourseController
/courses GET get all courses
/courses POST  adds new course
/courses/:id DELETE delete a specific course
/courses/:id/ GET get a specific course
/courses/:id/assignments GET get all course assignments
/courses/:id/assignments POST adds assignment to course
/courses/:id/students GET get all course students
/courses/:id/students POST adds a student to a course

AssignmentController
/assignments/:id GET get a specific assignment
/assignments/:id DELETE delete a specific assignment
/assignments/:id/submissions GET get all assignment submissions
/assignments/:id/submissions POST adds a submission to an assignment

SubmissionController
/submissions/:id GET get specific submission
/submissions/:id/grade POST update submission grade

